cutthroat island is a 1995 romantic comedy action adventure film directed by renny harlin and written by robert king and marc norman based on a story by michael frost beckner , james gorman , bruce a. evans , and raymond gideon .

movie directors : this finnish - born director hit it big with " die hard 2 " & " cliffhanger " ; then came " cutthroat island "

